Node_init_code:
MOV DWORD ECX, [ESP + 4]
	MOV DWORD [EAX + 16], ECX

guards.Nodehas:
MOV DWORD EDX, [ECX + 32]
CMP DWORD EDX, 1
JNE Node_has_succeed
guards.Nodeadd:
MOV DWORD EDX, [ECX + 32]
CMP DWORD EDX, 1
JNE Node_add_succeed
guards.NodeaddToChild:
MOV DWORD EDX, [ECX + 32]
CMP DWORD EDX, 1
JE Node_addToChild_succeed
